import {
  Box,
  Container,
  Text,
  Center,
  VStack,
  Input,
  Flex,
  FormControl,
  FormLabel,
  Button,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";

export const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Flex
      width="100vw"
      height="100vh"
      bgColor="#121214"
      direction="column"
      justify="center"
      align="center"
    >
      <Text color="#FF577F">Kenzie Hub</Text>
      <VStack spacing="15px">
        <form onSubmit={() => {}}>
          <FormControl>
            <VStack spacing="10px">
              <Box w="100%">
                <FormLabel color="#F8F9FA" fontSize="xs">
                  Email
                </FormLabel>
              </Box>
              <Input placeholder="Digite seu email" bg="#343B41" />
              <Box w="100%">
                <FormLabel color="#F8F9FA" fontSize="xs">
                  Senha
                </FormLabel>
              </Box>
              <Input placeholder="Digite sua senha" bg="#343B41" />
              <Button
                w="100%"
                mt="20px"
                bgColor="#FF577F"
                color="#FFF"
                type="submit"
              >
                Entrar
              </Button>
            </VStack>
          </FormControl>
        </form>
        <Box>
          <Text color="#868E96" fontSize="xs">
            Ainda nÃ£o possui uma conta?
          </Text>
        </Box>
      </VStack>
    </Flex>
  );
};
